Sabre managed to get a hand free to shake wheeljacks hand. "I'm Sabre 
leader of this group, the bird in my arms is WingRazor our bomb 
expert and coomunications tech, and the poor fellow over there with 
the hole in his chest plate is Rave who was a techie, and hacker."

Convoy smiled. "I am Convoy, Medical officer, and i believe now a 
Maximal. "It is a pleasure to meet all of you.

Sabre smiled and looked over to windlord and empath. "Um Jackie is 
it?" "Why not you show us they way back to the base, i believe these 
two really need a healing chamber, and..." He leaned towards 
WheelJack. "Those two look like they'd like to be alone." He smiled 
as he continued on...
